cc:Work.dc:description: A diagram showing four of the largest aircraft ever built, the Hughes H-4 Spruce Goose, the Antonov An-225 Mriya, the Boeing 747-8 Intercontinental, and the Airbus A380-800. The diagram is scaled at 10 px units per meter.
